rows.label: qst660203_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes, you. Your tales, your adventures...
Tell me of them, now, friend.

rows.label: qst660203_msg0003
rows.name:
Put to sweet music, your deeds shall
live on in infamy throughout the ages!
I'll throw in a little extra, too...

rows.label: qst660203_msg0004
rows.name: Tell tales for an Overdrive Protocol?

rows.label: qst660203_msg0102
rows.name:
Your deeds will go down in history, 
that's for sure.

rows.label: qst660203_msg0103
rows.name:
Ah, but in sooth, I am not sated!
Will this desire for tales of adventure
and derring-do ever abate?

rows.label: qst660203_msg0201
rows.name:
Too busy for telling stories, eh? 
I understand. The river of experience
e'er flows, and waits for none.

rows.label: qst660203_msg0202
rows.name:
But you will come back and speak with
me when you have time, yes?
